Class Sound

java.lang.Object
frc.gpws.Sound
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Sound
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Used in SoundManager as the base playable sound. Supports concatenating SoundManager.Sounds together to make many, many, many different sounds
